      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper describes Salmon's lightweight mapping procedure and quasi-mapping approach, but does not discuss comparing C++ and Rust implementations, boundary-case read classification via Smith-Waterman re-alignment, or disagreement resolution between mapper versions. The paper focuses on Salmon v0.8.0 (C++) benchmarking against kallisto and eXpress, not on cross-implementation validation.",
