      "asbval:note": "The paper describes Salmon as a transcript quantification tool but contains no discussion of C++ stream I/O bugs, buffer flushing issues, or debugging of output stream closure problems. The paper focuses on the algorithmic design and accuracy of Salmon's quantification methods, not on implementation-level debugging tasks.",
