      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms Salmon performs quantification via quasi-mapping or alignment input, but does not explicitly document that standard output/logs report 'total mapped and unmapped read counts' as a mapping-rate metric. The paper focuses on abundance estimates (TPM, \u03b7, \u03b1) rather than mapping rate reporting.",
