      "asbval:note": "The paper does not describe a workflow for validating cross-version or cross-implementation equivalence. The paper benchmarks Salmon against other tools (kallisto, eXpress) and validates accuracy on simulated and real data, but does not address version-to-version or implementation-to-implementation comparison for bug detection.",
