      "asbval:note": "The paper describes Salmon's quantification algorithm, bias models, and inference procedures (online/offline phases), but contains no discussion of SAM output verification, buffer flushing, stream closure, or data loss prevention. The paper does not address output stream management or SAM record validation workflows.",
