      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms Salmon performs read mapping via quasi-mapping or accepts pre-computed alignments in SAM/BAM format. However, the paper does not document Salmon writing SAM output files or any buffer flushing mechanism. The card conflates input (accepting SAM) with output (writing SAM).",
